  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t殴美白左对自己种族国家宗教政治经济人文文化教育信仰的卑鄙背叛：居然开门揖盗引狼入室，把与基督教血战上千年对基督教领土虎视眈眈充满憎恨一心报复必欲除之而后快的穆斯林，当作“移民”，“难民”，引入自己国土家园，任其繁衍胡闹越操越多，实现 <b>以 子宫 征服 异教 </b>的野心。这些殴美基督教民主自由的叛徒，真是叛国卖祖祸害苍生。我估计欧美基督教民主社会抵御清除自家门内日益猖狂放肆撒野发癫的穆斯林毒素，需要经历一个漫长痛苦甚至血腥的过程。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n整个地球最憎恨基督教也曾经与基督教打过无穷血战的宗教群裔，非穆斯林莫属。同时这个穆斯林宗教又是与当代西方民主自由宪政社会最不相容的垃圾原始野蛮意识形态。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n引狼入室又养虎为患的欧美傻瓜叛徒祸国殃民自取其辱自找灭亡：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9TTEt6eWk2LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLKzyi6.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLKzyi6.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SLKzyi6.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>血腥的残暴穆斯林：</b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9CekFUV2RRLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/BzATWdQ.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BzATWdQ.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BzATWdQ.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9wRmNNODM0LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/pFcM834.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/pFcM834.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pFcM834.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS82cmhoN1NZLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/6rhh7SY.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/6rhh7SY.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6rhh7SY.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n参看：<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/81574\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/81574\"><b>被穆斯林淹没的英国伦敦</b></a><br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/8732\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/87